WEBVTT

00:02.760 --> 00:04.880
Then don't blame elder brother for wronging you

00:05.840 --> 00:07.120
Though doing this

00:07.360 --> 00:08.800
Father will hate me

00:08.960 --> 00:10.760
History will condemn me

00:10.880 --> 00:11.960
But what can I do

00:12.480 --> 00:13.680
Our father has little fortune

00:13.800 --> 00:15.400
Only has us two sons

00:16.160 --> 00:17.920
Even if Father regrets

00:19.160 --> 00:20.800
It will be too late

00:24.600 --> 00:25.800
Do it cleanly

00:26.120 --> 00:27.440
How it's handled

00:27.800 --> 00:28.960
No need to tell me

00:30.800 --> 00:31.440
Your subject

00:31.760 --> 00:33.120
Bids farewell to the Crown Prince

00:38.160 --> 00:38.800
Let's go

00:39.360 --> 00:40.680
Let's go somewhere else
